title: ‘George Michael’s Snappy Snaps crash Range Rover’ for sale on eBay just months after ex-Wham! star’s tragic death
text:
Opinion PICK IT UP BEFORE IT GO GOES ‘George Michael’s Snappy Snaps crash Range Rover’ for sale on eBay just months after ex-Wham! star’s tragic death 
The seller claims they bought the car directly from the former Wham! star two years ago - and it's been in storage ever since Exclusive By GEMMA MULLIN AND JOHN SHAMMAS 22nd February 2017, 10:56 am
